  "texts": [
    "Contributions As far as we know, this work is the first to present an overview of explainable text summarization and to offer a dual perspective on how explainability and summarization can mutually contribute to each other.",
    "In the scope of this work, we use the terms related to explainability and interpretability interchangeably.",
    "The contributions of this survey are summarized as follows:",
    "• We review the current state of research on the intersection between explainability and text summarization.",
    "Our approach is twofold: we explore how explainability is applied to text summarization and how text summarization is utilized to enhance explainability."
  ],
